&lt;p&gt;Do you want to join our fantastic team of staff working in the lovely Lake district?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have Band 5 Pharmacy Technician vacancies ( 12 months fixed term contracts) at our Furness General Hospital Site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a Pharmacy Technician registered with the GPhC, you will hold an Accredited checking qualification, or willing to work towards within an agreed timeframe (Band 5 will be awarded upon satisfactory completion of training) and be proficient in medicines management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome full time and part time applications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours of work are 9am to 5.30pm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anyone newly appointed to the trust will be subject to the completion of a satisfactory 6 month probationary period (this includes bank staff). This will give the new staff member an opportunity to become familiar with the role and working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
